ComicInfo.Summary: SIP #53 marks the conclusion of a three-part story-within-a-story, "My Maiden Voyage." Someone has been killing Parker Girls one by one. FBI Special Agent Sara Bryan wants to know whom, and she's hoping Katchoo will tell her why. But Katchoo has more important things on her mind... like girl trouble! Things are getting hot in paradise!
